---
/**
 * Privacy-friendly, cookie-free analytics placeholder. Two options are stubbed;
 * the author activates ONE by uncommenting it and filling in the token. Neither
 * requires a consent banner. Google Analytics is intentionally not offered.
 *
 * The site's CSP (public/_headers) already allow-lists both script origins.
 */
---

{/* ── OPTION A (active): Cloudflare Web Analytics ── */}
<script
  defer
  src="https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js"
  data-cf-beacon='{"token": "e314b9cbfb614457938216b69d4b0bb4"}'
></script>

{/* ── OPTION B: GoatCounter ──
    ANALYTICS: replace 'CODE' with your GoatCounter site code after signing up
    at goatcounter.com
<script
  data-goatcounter="https://CODE.goatcounter.com/count"
  async
  src="//gc.zgo.at/count.js"
></script>
*/}
